{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">It is the near future of 2019, and you're trapped in a dome with 18,736 mad robots on the outskirts of a Las Vegas themed resort, and with only twenty minutes until a bomb wipes everything out. Race across a small open world, activate powerful buffs, and grow strong enough to survive the next danger, and maybe even escape <i>(Ed. Escape is not possible at this point in time)</i>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321790/extras/ExplorationFeaturesGif.gif?t=1738739348\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Explore </strong>the world.</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Discover Fountains to activate Buffs, Pylons to boost your character, and more</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Race to locations to gain experience</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Complete Time-Trials to increase the experience you earn</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321790/extras/CombatFeaturesGifBase7000-7505-ezgif.com-optimize__1_.gif?t=1738739348\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Explode</strong> the rustbuckets that have turned their attention to you.</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Utilise a variety of unique weapons to Wreck those Wrobots</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Deal Damage to destroy their puny frames</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Inflict Stun to weaken them, then ram into them to heal yourself</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Utilise Buffs to empower yourself and shape your run</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321790/extras/PermanentFeaturesGifBase7000-7348-ezgif.com-optimize.gif?t=1738739348\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Expire, </strong>and then try it all again.</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unlock Achievements to unlock new Weapons, Buffs, and improve your car's stats</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Discovered world features are added to your map permanently, letting you optimise your path through the world</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><br>If you haven't already, please consider checking out the Demo, it's a sizeable chunk of content, and will give you a very good idea if the game works for you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3321790?t=1738739348","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3321790?t=1738739348","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321790/395c0c5c7e2dec1d13db44ae93b8d58778d7f720/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738739348","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321790/395c0c5c7e2dec1d13db44ae93b8d58778d7f720/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1738739348","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Partial Controller Support","id":18},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"demos":[{"appid":3393250,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">It is the near future of 2019, and you're trapped in a dome with 18,736 mad robots on the outskirts of a Las Vegas themed resort, and with only twenty minutes until a bomb wipes everything out. Race across a small open world, activate powerful buffs, and grow strong enough to survive the next danger, and maybe even escape <i>(Ed. Escape is not possible at this point in time)</i>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://sh